title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
description: When setting a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com', the title of the hyperlink builder changes unexpectedly.
OB: The title of the hyperlink builder does not remain as 'Hyperlink Options' when setting a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should remain as 'Hyperlink Options' regardless of the hyperlink settings.
SR:
1. Open the hyperlink builder.
2. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
